<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">尾数逢9法，被乘数、乘数的尾数均为9。方法二，首先将两个乘数各自加1后相乘，其积扩大100倍；然后把两个乘数各自加1后相加的和（凑成齐头十位数）；最后加1×1，即为所求的积，可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(a+1-1)(b+1-1)=(a+1)(b+1)-(a+1)-(b+1)+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a、b分别为被乘数、乘数。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">79×69=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 79×69</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(79+1)×(69+1)-(79+1)-(69+1)+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=80×70-80-70+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=5600-150+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=5450+1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=5451</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>